name: MotorcycleSoundsforSleep
0:
”Alexa open motorcycle sounds”
”Alexa ask motorcycle sounds to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: motorcycle sounds
des:
Let the soft purr of a motorcycle engine lull you to sleep. Motorcycle Sounds is the ultimate science-backed companion for relaxation, focus, and better sleep. 

All you need to do is say Alexa start Motorcycle Sounds, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to leave on while you are asleep, to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
